stories_text_raw:
As a DataUser, I want to process deletions for a specific date, so that I can manage data effectively.

As a UIDesigner, I want to redesign the Resources page, so that it matches the new Broker design styles.

As a UIDesigner, I want to report user testing results to agencies, so that they are informed of user feedback.

As a UIDesigner, I want to begin user testing, so that I can validate stakeholder UI improvement requests.

As a UIDesigner, I want to schedule user testing, so that testers are informed and ready to participate.

As a UIDesigner, I want to track issues from Tech Thursday, so that I can address them in upcoming tests.

As a DevOpsEngineer, I want to set up New Relic, so that I can provide useful data across all applications.

As a BrokerUser, I want to sync D1 file generation with FPDS data load, so that the data remains consistent.

As a BrokerUser, I want to update error codes for submissions, so that submissions are processed correctly.

As a BrokerUser, I want to access published FABS files, so that I can retrieve necessary data.

As a BrokerUser, I want to create content mockups, so that data submission processes can be streamlined.

As a Developer, I want to update SQL codes, so that they are clearer and easier to maintain.

As a Developer, I want to log improvements, so that I can troubleshoot submission issues more effectively.

As a Developer, I want to index domain models, so that validation results can be retrieved faster.

As a Developer, I want to manage D Files generation requests, so that I can avoid duplicate performance issues.

As a Developer, I want to add GTAS window data to the database, so that the information is current and accessible.

As a Developer, I want to prevent duplicate submissions after refresh, so that data integrity is maintained.

As an AgencyUser, I want to map FederalActionObligation to Atom Feed, so that the data is properly organized.

As an AgencyUser, I want to ensure the header box shows updated date and time, so that users have accurate information.

As an AgencyUser, I want to check when submission periods start and end, so that I can manage deadlines effectively.

As a FABSUser, I want to access FABS data with read-only permissions, so that I can review it without making changes.

As a FABSUser, I want to submit citywide as PPoPZIP, so that I can ensure it passes validations.

As a FileUploadValidator, I want to validate submission files for correct file extensions, so that only valid files are processed.
